Package: negatr
Title: Negative Control Methods for Bias Detection and Correction
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Lorenzo", "Fabbri", , "lorenzo.fabbri92sm@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3031-322X"))
Description: A comprehensive framework for detecting and correcting biases in
    epidemiological studies using negative control exposures and outcomes.
    Supports methods for unmeasured confounding, selection bias, and
    measurement error, ranging from simple null hypothesis tests to
    proximal causal inference and empirical calibration.
